Here is my story.I got to know to coke studio Pakistan by the song 'allahu akbar'.I found the purest form of bliss in that.And now I'm your biggest fan.All songs are on my playlist and whenever I feel down listen the gems on a loop on and on.It has such great impact on me.If there is peace and bliss anywhere in the form of music, it's coke studio Pakistan.Love you from the core of my heart.
You have pure talents , dedication and passion which sums up in a magical environment.I am a singer too but don't know if I can reach to that level of perfection anyday.!
Being a singer , I know how much effort control and hours of dedication is needed to make a song perfect.
My only question is what's the problem with guys who are disliking, I mean 1K dislikes,seriously!!
we are surrounded by fools who don't know m of music and are disliking.
Come on.! This is pure music.!
shame on those poor kids.
Keep spreading love coke studio pakistan.
Warmest hug and endless love from your brother from India.💗
